import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['lat'], bins=20)
    plt.xlabel('Latitude')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of latitudes in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    key_counts = data['key'].value_counts()
    key_counts.plot(kind='bar')
    plt.xlabel('Keys')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of keys in the dataset?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    average_latitude = data['lat'].mean()
    plt.axhline(y=average_latitude, color='r', linestyle='-', label=f'Average Latitude: {average_latitude:.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the average latitude in the dataset?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['key'].plot(kind='hist', bins=50)
    min_key = data['key'].min()
    max_key = data['key'].max()
    plt.axvline(min_key, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Min Key: {min_key:.2f}')
    plt.axvline(max_key, color='g', linestyle='--', label=f'Max Key: {max_key:.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the range of keys in the dataset?")
    plt.xlabel("Keys")
    plt.ylabel("Frequency")
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
